{{Quote|People are always getting me confused with [[Dark Fighter]].|[[Final Fantasy I & II: Dawn of Souls]], in [[Final Fantasy|the former title]]'s [[Whisperwind Cove (Final_Fantasy)|Whisperwind Cove]]}}
The '''Dark Wizard''', also known as the '''MAGE''', is an enemy in ''[[Final Fantasy]]''. Appearing in the [[Cavern of Ice]] and the [[Chaos Shrine (Final Fantasy)|Chaos Shrine]], they are powerful spellcasters capable of casting several high-level [[Black Magic]] spells, and may appear alongside their [[White Magic]] counterpart, the [[Dark Fighter]].

