== Battle ==
The Dark Wizard uses powerful black magic spells capable of hitting the entire party and/or inflicting [[instant death]]. It is particularly dangerous in the NES release, where [[Death (Final Fantasy)|Death]] is always the first spell it casts at a time when the party does not have access to protection from [[Instant Death (Final Fantasy)|Instant Death]]. However, the Wizard is also frail and will quickly go down to any attack.

